# AT_CHECK_JAVA_MINIMAL([DIRECTIVES], [PARSER_ACTION], [POSITION_CLASS])
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Check that a minimal parser with DIRECTIVES compiles in Java.
# Put the Java code in YYParser.java.
